article_title: What The House ObamaCare Lawsuit And 'King v. Burwell' Have In Common

article_metadata.description: King v. Burwell would knock out two legs of the PPACA's three-legged stool in 36 states. House v. Burwell would shorten one of those legs in all 50 states.
article_metadata.author: Michael F. Cannon
